message: "If you use DDSync in your research, please cite the software using the citation below."
title: "DDSync: Graph-based denoising of differential travel-time observations"
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: "Heimisson"
    given-names: "Elías Rafn"
    affiliation: "Institute of Earth Sciences, University of Iceland"
    orcid: "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-8342-7226"   # optional
